Class MyToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.CommonToken

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class MyToken
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.CommonToken
implements java.lang.Comparable<MyToken>
    A class wrapping ANTLR's CommonToken with a reference to the FileBuffer it originated from.
